MABEL BLANCHE YOUNG SMITH, by her husband and next friend, WILBUR CURTIS SMITH, v. CAROLYN CHERBINO, joined by her husband, JEROME CHERBINO, individually, and MRS. L. M. PLATT, a widow. 15 So. (2nd) 764

June Term, 1943

December 7, 1943 En Banc Boone & Boone and David B. Newsom, for appellant. Rinehart & Carroll, for appellees. *753PER CURIAM:

Affirmed.

BUFORD, C. J., CHAPMAN, THOMAS, ADAMS and SE-BRING, JJ., concur. TERRELL and BROWN, JJ., dissent.
